hopobject.body: Where do you study? pharmarelations denmark This time 12 months ago Ainslie was preparing for a fifth straight Olympic Games, on home waters in Weymouth. He was applying himself with characteristic intensity to the pursuit of a fourth Olympic gold, which would make him the most successful Olympic sailor in history. A heavy favourite, the pressure on him was almost unbearable. It dominated his every waking thought. Everything else in his life was pushed to one side.
